WEBVTT

NOTE Video ID: 4xUPmrEvurY

NOTE Language: en

00:00:01.849 --> 00:00:12.770
Now for puja, one has to understand that without
Realisation, puja has no meaning, because

00:00:12.770 --> 00:00:15.680
you are not ananya.

00:00:15.680 --> 00:00:26.610
Is, you have to become aware of your whole.

00:00:26.610 --> 00:00:30.340
Krishna’s description of Bhakti is ananya.

00:00:30.340 --> 00:00:42.780
He says, “I will give you ananya bhakti”,
He wants ananya bhakti, means when there is

00:00:42.780 --> 00:00:46.800
not the other, means when we are realised.

00:00:46.800 --> 00:00:54.370
Otherwise He says “Pushpam, phalam toyum”
(Bhagavad Gita verse 26) “A flower, a fruit

00:00:54.370 --> 00:01:04.600
and a water: whatever you give me I accept”
But when it comes to giving, He says, “You

00:01:04.600 --> 00:01:13.280
have to come to Me with ananya bhakti,”
means: when you have become

00:01:13.280 --> 00:01:21.210
one with Me, then you should have the devotion,
not before that.

00:01:21.210 --> 00:01:25.640
Before that, you are not connected.

00:01:25.640 --> 00:01:28.439
Now puja is the left hand side projection.

00:01:28.439 --> 00:01:35.250
It’s the neutralisation of the right side,
very much.

00:01:35.250 --> 00:01:41.020
Specially for people who are very right handed,
atmosphere which is very right handed, puja

00:01:41.020 --> 00:01:42.969
is ideal for them.

00:01:42.969 --> 00:01:51.840
Is the bhakti, is the devotion…that you
project.

00:01:51.840 --> 00:02:08.530
Now what happens actually when you project
this puja?

00:02:08.530 --> 00:02:12.800
It has been found out, and now as I am telling
you, that first you have to awaken within

00:02:12.800 --> 00:02:22.630
you the Deities that are still asleep, by
worshipping them.

00:02:22.630 --> 00:02:31.640
But as these Deities, Primordial Deities,
are with Me, you worship Me, and every Deity

00:02:31.640 --> 00:02:34.590
in Me is awakened, by which your Deities are
awakened.

00:02:34.590 --> 00:02:39.070
So first, your vibrations must improve, to
receive.

00:02:39.070 --> 00:02:49.290
If the reception is not good what’s the
use of any puja or projection?

00:02:49.290 --> 00:02:56.630
So first of all we, sort of, prepare our instrument,
or prepare our projecting instrument.

00:02:56.630 --> 00:03:07.010
That preparation is done by praying to different
Deities, as we call that: a Kundalini puja.

00:03:07.010 --> 00:03:13.390
By praying to My Kundalini you improve your
reflection.

00:03:13.390 --> 00:03:22.230
Because then the vibrations from Me start
flowing into yours and they awaken it.

00:03:22.230 --> 00:03:31.680
This is the projection as far as you are concerned.

00:03:31.680 --> 00:03:36.570
Once the instrument is alright, then you project
outside.

00:03:36.570 --> 00:03:42.500
And now how do you project?

00:03:42.500 --> 00:03:58.490
By worshipping the Goddess as the Protector
of the whole Universe, praising Her different

00:03:58.490 --> 00:04:08.850
attributes, even Her Face, Her Hands, everything
has a meaning.

00:04:08.850 --> 00:04:11.960
Praising Her Powers.

00:04:11.960 --> 00:04:22.500
By saying that, by repeating that, you echo
in your projection Her Powers, and then your

00:04:22.500 --> 00:04:24.540
projection becomes that powerful.

00:04:24.540 --> 00:04:33.290
It’s a very subtle happening that takes
place, it’s miraculous.

00:04:33.290 --> 00:04:40.850
These things look so simple, like just like
washing my Feet.

00:04:40.850 --> 00:04:42.100
Simple thing is washing my Feet.

00:04:42.100 --> 00:04:48.600
Now see these Feet, I don’t know if you
see, the whole Universe I see there and I

00:04:48.600 --> 00:04:52.530
really get stunned by them.

00:04:52.530 --> 00:04:57.140
When you wash My Feet, what do you do?

00:04:57.140 --> 00:05:02.490
Actually, My Feet have been working very hard.

00:05:02.490 --> 00:05:11.630
And then you put a little water to soothe
them, to suggest that you can feel the effort

00:05:11.630 --> 00:05:12.870
put in by these Feet.

00:05:12.870 --> 00:05:20.990
And a kind of a very sweet, melodious love
flows out of these Feet there.

00:05:20.990 --> 00:05:26.060
Like today I was coming, and I suddenly saw
Paul (Winter) standing.

00:05:26.060 --> 00:05:28.080
Same thing happened to me.

00:05:28.080 --> 00:05:35.110
See, what a care it is, what an understanding,
“Mother is coming, She should not be lost!”

00:05:35.110 --> 00:05:40.120
Just that, and the thing started melting.

00:05:40.120 --> 00:05:49.080
Because this love who understands everything,
doesn’t want anything, but is only excited

00:05:49.080 --> 00:05:51.960
if there is somebody to receive the love.

00:05:51.960 --> 00:05:54.620
Now how do you say you are going to receive?

00:05:54.620 --> 00:06:00.610
By expressing these small-small things.

00:06:00.610 --> 00:06:09.460
So when you soothe My Feet, wash Them, clean
Them, you know what They mean: you recognise.

00:06:09.460 --> 00:06:12.919
That recognition, how are you to show?

00:06:12.919 --> 00:06:17.889
You see, these ceremonies, little ceremonies
are important because they express your recognition.

00:06:17.889 --> 00:06:25.810
It could be absolutely dull, dead and finished,
and it could be absolutely living, if you

00:06:25.810 --> 00:06:29.120
know why you are doing it.

00:06:29.120 --> 00:06:37.560
Then you apply some oil and things [to] again
soothe My Feet.

00:06:37.560 --> 00:06:43.970
Just say, “Mother, You have worked very
hard, Your Feet have worked very hard."

00:06:43.970 --> 00:06:50.670
Just saying that itself, I mean makes no difference
otherwise, if you say in a very rational manner,

00:06:50.670 --> 00:06:56.840
but to that Love that are these Feet it makes
a very big difference.

00:06:56.840 --> 00:07:03.520
There is sweetness: a little thing, a little
baby just puts her hand on her mother’s

00:07:03.520 --> 00:07:11.949
cheeks, you see, just to express the gratitude,
and the mother’s heart starts jumping with

00:07:11.949 --> 00:07:12.949
love.

00:07:12.949 --> 00:07:23.790
It is a very reciprocal behaviour, it’s
very subtle and that kind of a subtle working

00:07:23.790 --> 00:07:33.270
is fixed already: it works that way only.

00:07:33.270 --> 00:07:35.930
The more you love from your heart, the more
the joy will be there.

00:07:35.930 --> 00:07:45.220
The more you are rational and more mental,
there won’t be so much joy.

00:07:45.220 --> 00:07:51.330
It should be [that] first of all your cleansing
is important but the projection should be

00:07:51.330 --> 00:07:58.240
towards your Mother, that is the height.

00:07:58.240 --> 00:08:10.130
Once you achieve that height, then you become
all-powerful, and then you can give to others.

00:08:10.130 --> 00:08:21.150
But that giving is nothing but is a very,
very, as I told you is a very mutual and absolutely

00:08:21.150 --> 00:08:22.150
reciprocal.

00:08:22.150 --> 00:08:25.830
Because the Devi knows about you, everything.

00:08:25.830 --> 00:08:32.460
If you are trying anything else, She knows
and She will also tell you frankly that this

00:08:32.460 --> 00:08:37.289
should not be done, that should not be done,
should not be done, clearly, so that you do

00:08:37.289 --> 00:08:40.579
not be under any misunderstandings about it.

00:08:40.579 --> 00:08:46.149
But still, to work it out, you must know it
has to be reciprocal, it cannot be one-sided.

00:08:46.149 --> 00:08:58.699
The sincerity cannot be one-sided, it has
to be both sides, then it works out better.

00:08:58.699 --> 00:09:10.850
And a kind of a homogeneous feeling with that
Love comes in, sort of a lubricant, a beautiful

00:09:10.850 --> 00:09:17.610
feeling of movement within yourself comes
in.

00:09:17.610 --> 00:09:23.009
Puja really is the triggering thing, it triggers
you.

00:09:23.009 --> 00:09:30.160
It triggers you into another realm, it’s
really miraculous.

00:09:30.160 --> 00:09:34.430
Once you have done the puja then you can project
out, much more, in your silence only.

00:09:34.430 --> 00:09:39.620
Your silence itself becomes so powerful.

00:09:39.620 --> 00:09:49.199
Now in this special case of our Western lives,
we have to established our innocence, very

00:09:49.199 --> 00:09:55.220
important, it is the first thing that is attacked,
innocence is attacked by so many things.

00:09:55.220 --> 00:09:59.269
So we have to established our innocence.

00:09:59.269 --> 00:10:04.740
And innocence is the most powerful thing:
it doesn’t see anything bad, it doesn’t

00:10:04.740 --> 00:10:10.069
see anything wrong, it doesn’t see anything…It
loves, just goes on loving, innocence.

00:10:10.069 --> 00:10:13.740
A child doesn’t know that the mother hates
the child.

00:10:13.740 --> 00:10:18.059
The child doesn’t know if anybody hates.

00:10:18.059 --> 00:10:19.819
In innocence they live.

00:10:19.819 --> 00:10:26.110
And then they suddenly discover sometimes,
they are shocked, how people are!

00:10:26.110 --> 00:10:30.920
They don’t love!

00:10:30.920 --> 00:10:35.730
They don’t love.

00:10:35.730 --> 00:10:37.570
So Ganesha is very important for the Western
countries, very important, because that’s

00:10:37.570 --> 00:10:46.110
the essence of everything, I think, that’s
the most essential thing.

00:10:46.110 --> 00:10:49.790
That’s why we worship Ganesha first.

00:10:49.790 --> 00:10:59.069
And Ganesha was created first of all, because
He is the eldest son, He’s the first son.

00:10:59.069 --> 00:11:15.310
He’s the eldest brother you have, and though
Kumara (Kartikeya) is treated as an elder

00:11:15.310 --> 00:11:24.589
brother always, while Ganesha calls Himself
as a younger brother, though He was the first

00:11:24.589 --> 00:11:27.279
created!

00:11:27.279 --> 00:11:29.839
Because He remains young always, never grows.

00:11:29.839 --> 00:11:35.420
So in a way, He’s always younger to you
also.

00:11:35.420 --> 00:11:42.319
It’s a very, very subtle understanding:
a very young little thing is so much wiser.

00:11:42.319 --> 00:11:43.319
He is wisdom.

00:11:43.319 --> 00:11:46.470
Can you imagine a little baby is so intelligent.

00:11:46.470 --> 00:11:49.350
A little baby so wise?

00:11:49.350 --> 00:12:01.410
Much more, He’s like a grown-up little baby,
a very matured, wise, little baby.

00:12:01.410 --> 00:12:13.639
So by age, you are always older than Him,
but by wisdom, He is the eldest.

00:12:13.639 --> 00:12:20.379
Then like this you should understand how we
evoke all the Deities within us by doing these

00:12:20.379 --> 00:12:23.279
small things, by saying Their mantras.

00:12:23.279 --> 00:12:28.589
Because now you are awakened, every word you
say is awakened now, is siddha mantra.

00:12:28.589 --> 00:12:37.519
On this Guru puja I’m really going to give
you the way of how to do the siddhartha is

00:12:37.519 --> 00:12:49.509
the establishment of the siddha.

00:12:49.509 --> 00:12:51.709
To master.

00:12:51.709 --> 00:12:57.079
To master every chakra and every deity bestowed
upon it.

00:12:57.079 --> 00:13:02.259
To master it, how to do it, I will tell you
this Guru puja no doubt.

00:13:02.259 --> 00:13:03.679
Going to work it out.

00:13:03.679 --> 00:13:15.189
But this puja is to be done with full understanding,
and with full recognition that it’s a great

00:13:15.189 --> 00:13:16.199
fortune.

00:13:16.199 --> 00:13:22.290
Even the Devas are jealous of you, all the
rishis are jealous of you, so many people

00:13:22.290 --> 00:13:24.250
are jealous of you.

00:13:24.250 --> 00:13:29.610
The greatest advantage for you, greatest fortune.

00:13:29.610 --> 00:13:34.029
Make full use of it.

00:13:34.029 --> 00:13:38.439
And they are very simple things that can please,
very simple.

00:13:38.439 --> 00:13:43.079
You know your Mother can be pleased with very,
very simple things.

00:13:43.079 --> 00:13:44.850
It’s like that only.

00:13:44.850 --> 00:13:51.610
It’s how much heart you have put into it,
is the point.

00:13:51.610 --> 00:13:55.689
I think tomorrow we should have the puja,
today we have understood about it.

00:13:55.689 --> 00:14:01.279
It is more to be felt and understood and realised
than to be thought about.

00:14:01.279 --> 00:14:03.689
Because you’ll go into thoughtless awareness.

00:14:03.689 --> 00:14:06.089
It is more source of triggering.

00:14:06.089 --> 00:14:12.509
For example, I think I’ll ask Hari (Jairam)
to give the miracle we had yesterday, would

00:14:12.509 --> 00:14:13.790
be [a] good idea.

00:14:13.790 --> 00:14:22.179
On our way we were coming, from…he was losing
his way throughout, and Regis (Camille) was

00:14:22.179 --> 00:14:28.059
navigating him (laughter) so we were all lost!

00:14:28.059 --> 00:14:34.980
But then we had a miracle while coming back:
there was in M1 (road) a complete jam and

00:14:34.980 --> 00:14:39.470
miles together we could see there is no movement.

00:14:39.470 --> 00:14:44.550
And suddenly, within two minutes, what happened,
what I told him, and how he worked it out.

00:14:44.550 --> 00:14:49.100
Hari has a problem you see, I think Felicity
(Payment) has the same mad problem.

00:14:49.100 --> 00:14:50.100
Where is she?

00:14:50.100 --> 00:14:51.100
Is she there?

00:14:51.100 --> 00:14:52.100
Yes?

00:14:52.100 --> 00:14:54.569
You see, like, to get after everything, to
do it…

00:14:54.569 --> 00:14:58.579
Now he thought that I have told that you put
your attention inside.

00:14:58.579 --> 00:15:06.850
Now he has a slope in his left side, as she
has too, and when you do it too much inside,

00:15:06.850 --> 00:15:08.529
you go on the slope.

00:15:08.529 --> 00:15:13.799
So Hari being a wiser person in this respect
because he’s not been a psychologist, he

00:15:13.799 --> 00:15:19.079
does not do that much, but Felicity does that,
is to go over do it.

00:15:19.079 --> 00:15:24.110
I mean she goes down very very deep into her
subconscious.

00:15:24.110 --> 00:15:27.320
While Hari understands there’s something’s
going wrong.

00:15:27.320 --> 00:15:30.769
I never said that you get after anything.

00:15:30.769 --> 00:15:35.859
Now, “put your attention inside” means:
if you get Realisation by that.

00:15:35.859 --> 00:15:39.689
If you don’t get Realisation, there’s
something wrong somewhere, you have lost your

00:15:39.689 --> 00:15:43.690
way, that’s the main point is.

00:15:43.690 --> 00:15:48.369
So I told Hari that, “You don’t put your
attention inside because you go on the slope,

00:15:48.369 --> 00:15:51.929
your car is such that it doesn’t go the
other way round, it goes into the slope, doesn’t

00:15:51.929 --> 00:15:54.819
go to the heart.

00:15:54.819 --> 00:16:00.730
So best thing is that now you [should] become
active outside and forget about it (the inside).

00:16:00.730 --> 00:16:03.279
And after some time you’ll receive a balance."

00:16:03.279 --> 00:16:05.079
I said “At this point.."

00:16:05.079 --> 00:16:08.279
Now he was trying to worry about the traffic.

00:16:08.279 --> 00:16:09.279
The other Mr.

00:16:09.279 --> 00:16:12.199
‘Navigator’ (Regis) was also busy worrying
about it!

00:16:12.199 --> 00:16:17.810
So I said, “Now, just now, you do not pay
any attention anywhere, you just project outside

00:16:17.810 --> 00:16:23.829
and think of everyone, how we are going to
get them realised” Only I said like this,

00:16:23.829 --> 00:16:24.829
and he started doing it.

00:16:24.829 --> 00:16:28.639
I said, “You never see the trees, you never
do this” And then what happened?

00:16:28.639 --> 00:16:29.639
You tell.

00:16:29.639 --> 00:16:30.639
Within 2 minutes time?

00:16:30.639 --> 00:16:34.170
Everybody, Chaya (Camille, Regis’ wife)
was there, all of them.

00:16:34.170 --> 00:16:37.709
Suddenly they found that the whole M1 (road)
was empty and they were rushing fast, you

00:16:37.709 --> 00:16:38.709
see.

00:16:38.709 --> 00:16:42.139
There was not, hardly one or two cars.

00:16:42.139 --> 00:16:45.319
The whole M1 was emptied, absolutely!

00:16:45.319 --> 00:16:49.500
And they did not know how it happened.

00:16:49.500 --> 00:16:50.850
Just they were there.

00:16:50.850 --> 00:16:53.339
And none of the things that we were going….

00:16:53.339 --> 00:16:57.109
Ray Harris: Was that yesterday afternoon on
the M1 Mother?

00:16:57.109 --> 00:16:59.239
Shri Mataji: Not today, yesterday

00:16:59.239 --> 00:17:00.239
Ray: Yesterday.

00:17:00.239 --> 00:17:05.010
Because I was on a coach there, and we were
in the traffic jam.

00:17:05.010 --> 00:17:11.139
Shri Mataji: Means you were in the traffic
jam! (laughter) The whole traffic jam

00:17:11.139 --> 00:17:16.779
Ray: We were 1 mile from the exit and it stopped
dead.

00:17:16.779 --> 00:17:22.720
And then we stayed there and suddenly it cleared
and there were no cars! (laughter)

00:17:22.720 --> 00:17:26.579
Shri Mataji: Suddenly the whole thing cleared
up!

00:17:26.579 --> 00:17:29.309
And suddenly, and they realised, and they
didn’t know how it cleared up.

00:17:29.309 --> 00:17:30.740
He speeded the car, I said “How?”

00:17:30.740 --> 00:17:35.960
He said, “The car, I don’t know” and
all the things that were in front of us, and

00:17:35.960 --> 00:17:38.340
all that, God knows where they disappeared
[to]!

00:17:38.340 --> 00:17:43.850
Such huge big things and on the sides and
this and that.

00:17:43.850 --> 00:17:44.980
Nothing!

00:17:44.980 --> 00:17:50.130
This is what is maya that upsets you.

00:17:50.130 --> 00:17:52.530
Project yourself outside.

00:17:52.530 --> 00:18:00.530
There was another experience I told these
people was this: that there were two journalists,

00:18:00.530 --> 00:18:01.530
one Mr.

00:18:01.530 --> 00:18:05.399
Marathe and a friend who are Sahaja Yogis,
and I went to the journalist’s association,

00:18:05.399 --> 00:18:06.880
they had a meeting.

00:18:06.880 --> 00:18:11.059
And there is another one who told Me, “No,
no Mother I have complete faith in You because

00:18:11.059 --> 00:18:15.070
there was a miracle that happened to a friend
of mine, Marathe, who is a Sahaja Yogi."

00:18:15.070 --> 00:18:16.200
I said, “What happened?”

00:18:16.200 --> 00:18:25.470
He said they were coming, by, from Poona down
to Bombay, and their brakes failed, and the

00:18:25.470 --> 00:18:29.350
slopes, you see, on the ghats (mountains),
it moves very fast.

00:18:29.350 --> 00:18:34.240
And suddenly they saw a huge big truck coming
up, with all the lights on top, and they didn’t

00:18:34.240 --> 00:18:36.159
know how to control, and they were about to
dash out.

00:18:36.159 --> 00:18:39.659
Just they closed their eyes and they said,
“Now, Mother, save us!”

00:18:39.659 --> 00:18:48.110
And suddenly they found that the car had crossed
the thing, and the thing was moving upwards,

00:18:48.110 --> 00:18:49.140
the truck was moving.

00:18:49.140 --> 00:18:56.600
They didn’t know, as if somebody had picked
up that car and put it on the other side.

00:18:56.600 --> 00:19:01.910
So these miracles can work out in case you
project yourself out.

00:19:01.910 --> 00:19:06.630
But for projecting outside, first you should
be cleansed inside.

00:19:06.630 --> 00:19:12.210
But for that also, all the time if your attention
[is like this -] “where am I catching?”

00:19:12.210 --> 00:19:13.720
Then you go onto rationality.

00:19:13.720 --> 00:19:18.929
“I must be catching because of this, I must
be catching because of that."

00:19:18.929 --> 00:19:24.850
I have told you hundred times not to say ‘why’.

00:19:24.850 --> 00:19:28.590
Give up this word ‘why’.

00:19:28.590 --> 00:19:31.580
“Why am I catching?”

00:19:31.580 --> 00:19:34.570
It will settle down.

00:19:34.570 --> 00:19:37.110
This maddening must go away!

00:19:37.110 --> 00:19:43.820
You cannot answer ‘why’ of anything in
Sahaja Yoga, can you?

00:19:43.820 --> 00:19:47.210
“Why did I meet you?”, “Why did you
get Realisation?”

00:19:47.210 --> 00:19:54.760
Ask hundred questions, two hundred, three
hundred, five hundred – you will not have

00:19:54.760 --> 00:19:55.760
any answer!

00:19:55.760 --> 00:19:57.350
So give up that.

00:19:57.350 --> 00:20:08.990
It’s not your rationality, it’s the Grace,
it’s the whim of the Grace that’s working

00:20:08.990 --> 00:20:11.760
it out!

00:20:11.760 --> 00:20:21.090
What are you trying at?

00:20:21.090 --> 00:20:23.950
Just ask for the Grace.

00:20:23.950 --> 00:20:24.950
Finished!

00:20:24.950 --> 00:20:25.950
It’s silent.

00:20:25.950 --> 00:20:26.950
It works out.

00:20:26.950 --> 00:20:27.950
This is maddening!

00:20:27.950 --> 00:20:28.950
You’ll become mad people.

00:20:28.950 --> 00:20:30.429
This is the greatest madness that people want
to know why of everything.

00:20:30.429 --> 00:20:31.960
How can you understand?

00:20:31.960 --> 00:20:36.380
You don’t have that chitti to understand
it.

00:20:36.380 --> 00:20:38.221
“[Mother] Can you explain?”

00:20:38.221 --> 00:20:39.221
How can I?

00:20:39.221 --> 00:20:43.400
If you make a little ant understand human
civilisation and this dirty politics you play

00:20:43.400 --> 00:20:44.400
it may understand.

00:20:44.400 --> 00:20:46.240
But you cannot understand ‘why’ of God.

00:20:46.240 --> 00:20:47.380
This is the relationship.

00:20:47.380 --> 00:20:53.960
So now, you give it up asking questions like
that.

00:20:53.960 --> 00:20:59.940
It’s too tremendous for this rationality.

00:20:59.940 --> 00:21:02.340
“Why God is doing?

00:21:02.340 --> 00:21:03.649
How He does?

00:21:03.649 --> 00:21:04.940
What are His powers?”

00:21:04.940 --> 00:21:10.519
Only thing [you can do] as scientists, you
note down – “Yes, it is so, yes, it is

00:21:10.519 --> 00:21:12.320
so, yes it is so."

00:21:12.320 --> 00:21:13.789
Verify it and note down.

00:21:13.789 --> 00:21:18.820
Only your awareness is changed from the scientist,
that you can see subtler working.

00:21:18.820 --> 00:21:20.110
But why it works?

00:21:20.110 --> 00:21:21.110
That’s His whim!

00:21:21.110 --> 00:21:22.110
He’ll do what He likes!

00:21:22.110 --> 00:21:25.940
Who are you to question God?

00:21:25.940 --> 00:21:28.260
How can you question God?

00:21:28.260 --> 00:21:37.410
Just give up asking this question ‘why’
and you will feel very much better.

00:21:37.410 --> 00:21:40.330
“It is God, you see, He does it!”

00:21:40.330 --> 00:21:41.640
This is what is faith.

00:21:41.640 --> 00:21:44.500
Not the blind, but real [faith], with understanding.

00:21:44.500 --> 00:21:50.509
I have told you this story of My grandmother
many a times, as she used to tell Me about

00:21:50.509 --> 00:21:55.919
faith, and which I have repeated to you so
many times, but again I’ll repeat it today:

00:21:55.919 --> 00:22:02.750
There were three people at different places,
and one man was going to see God.

00:22:02.750 --> 00:22:04.960
So they came to know about it.

00:22:04.960 --> 00:22:13.200
So one of them was in the forest, standing
on his head, doing all kinds of yogas and

00:22:13.200 --> 00:22:20.529
things like that, and praying to God – must
be with both hands towards Him, and soaking

00:22:20.529 --> 00:22:28.360
the feet, may be – like mad, you see, and
asking, “Why don’t You meet me?

00:22:28.360 --> 00:22:29.980
Why don’t You meet me?

00:22:29.980 --> 00:22:34.529
I want to meet You! why don’t you meet me?”

00:22:34.529 --> 00:22:39.000
And the man who was going to see God went
through that side, and He said, “Now please

00:22:39.000 --> 00:22:40.960
go and ask Him why don’t You come and see
me?

00:22:40.960 --> 00:22:43.519
You better come and see me, Why don’t You
do it?”

00:22:43.519 --> 00:22:50.299
So he said, “Alright, I’ll come, I’m
sorry” He had become thin, you see, absolutely

00:22:50.299 --> 00:22:52.720
thinned down, condition very miserable.

00:22:52.720 --> 00:22:59.700
He said, “Alright, I’ll go and tell God
about you."

00:22:59.700 --> 00:23:05.440
So, then he went up to God, no, no, before
that.

00:23:05.440 --> 00:23:14.909
Then he met another type who was sitting on
the street, and will be at the street side,

00:23:14.909 --> 00:23:15.909
and he said, “Oh!

00:23:15.909 --> 00:23:17.419
I heard you are going to meet God?”

00:23:17.419 --> 00:23:20.769
He said: yes, he is going to meet God.

00:23:20.769 --> 00:23:24.880
So he said, “Then communicate one small
little thing."

00:23:24.880 --> 00:23:27.940
He said, “What?”

00:23:27.940 --> 00:23:36.360
He said that, “Just tell Him I have had
no food, please send me my food now, I’m

00:23:36.360 --> 00:23:37.360
hungry."

00:23:37.360 --> 00:23:38.440
He said “What?”

00:23:38.440 --> 00:23:42.070
“Yes, you just tell Him that much."

00:23:42.070 --> 00:23:43.070
So he went up.

00:23:43.070 --> 00:23:44.070
He saw God.

00:23:44.070 --> 00:23:45.070
So God asked, “Did you meet some people
on your way?”

00:23:45.070 --> 00:23:47.570
He said, “Yes, I met a horrible one who
is all time saying ‘Why not?

00:23:47.570 --> 00:23:48.570
Why this?”

00:23:48.570 --> 00:23:50.789
And “Why?”, “Should I do it and should
I not?’

00:23:50.789 --> 00:23:54.149
And this and that, is going on.

00:23:54.149 --> 00:23:57.011
So, will You go and meet him?

00:23:57.011 --> 00:23:58.011
He’s asking."

00:23:58.011 --> 00:24:03.419
He (God) said, “No, better tell him to do
it little more, you see… still he has to

00:24:03.419 --> 00:24:04.419
do.

00:24:04.419 --> 00:24:05.419
He requires more effort.

00:24:05.419 --> 00:24:06.419
He won’t be satisfied.

00:24:06.419 --> 00:24:09.730
Till he gives up his efforts, let him go on."

00:24:09.730 --> 00:24:12.350
I mean he would have become mad like that.

00:24:12.350 --> 00:24:14.830
But now God says, “Alright, let him go ahead!

00:24:14.830 --> 00:24:15.830
What to do?

00:24:15.830 --> 00:24:16.830
If you tell them, they don’t want to listen,
so let them go ahead."

00:24:16.830 --> 00:24:23.200
Then he said, “Then I met another mad fellow,
who was on the street, he said that ‘ I’m

00:24:23.200 --> 00:24:25.410
hungry, ask God to send some food for me.

00:24:25.410 --> 00:24:26.410
Please ask.

00:24:26.410 --> 00:24:28.510
Tell God that I’m hungry.’

00:24:28.510 --> 00:24:29.510
” He (God) said, “Really?”

00:24:29.510 --> 00:24:30.510
He called all His managers He said, “Please
send his food.

00:24:30.510 --> 00:24:31.510
Have you not yet arranged his food and all
that?

00:24:31.510 --> 00:24:32.510
Please arrange it."

00:24:32.510 --> 00:24:34.100
He was quite surprised.

00:24:34.100 --> 00:24:36.160
He said, “What is this?

00:24:36.160 --> 00:24:41.730
This man is just telling ‘I’m hungry’,
and God is so much worried about this fellow

00:24:41.730 --> 00:24:45.549
and not worried about the fellow who is standing
on his head and asking such a lot of questions

00:24:45.549 --> 00:24:46.549
to God."

00:24:46.549 --> 00:24:53.330
So God knows everything, so He told him, “Now,
alright you are going down, you just tell

00:24:53.330 --> 00:24:57.490
them one story to both of them, and see their
reactions, and then you will know."

00:24:57.490 --> 00:24:59.330
So He told him a story.

00:24:59.330 --> 00:25:08.330
“You tell them that, ‘I went to God and
saw there, God passing a camel through the

00:25:08.330 --> 00:25:12.409
eye of a needle.’ ” and he said, “Really?”

00:25:12.409 --> 00:25:17.010
He said, “Yes, you go and tell them."

00:25:17.010 --> 00:25:18.750
So he came down.

00:25:18.750 --> 00:25:21.790
This fellow was still on his head.

00:25:21.790 --> 00:25:24.840
He came back, “What did God say?”

00:25:24.840 --> 00:25:28.360
He said you have to go on still for some time."

00:25:28.360 --> 00:25:29.360
He said, “Oh!

00:25:29.360 --> 00:25:30.360
Really?

00:25:30.360 --> 00:25:31.360
Well all glory to God!”

00:25:31.360 --> 00:25:32.380
He said, “Yes, he said so."

00:25:32.380 --> 00:25:33.380
He said, “Really?”

00:25:33.380 --> 00:25:35.149
Then, “Did you see something special there?”

00:25:35.149 --> 00:25:39.509
He said, “Yes, I saw that He passed a camel
through the eye of a needle!”

00:25:39.509 --> 00:25:43.299
He said, “No, no, don’t tell me stories!

00:25:43.299 --> 00:25:45.200
How can it?

00:25:45.200 --> 00:25:47.340
Such a big camel!

00:25:47.340 --> 00:25:48.890
How can it pass through the eye?

00:25:48.890 --> 00:25:50.559
After all it’s impossible!

00:25:50.559 --> 00:25:51.809
It is impossible!

00:25:51.809 --> 00:25:53.059
This is impossible!

00:25:53.059 --> 00:25:55.440
You are just now trying to befool me.

00:25:55.440 --> 00:25:58.470
Because you have been to God you think you
can befool me.

00:25:58.470 --> 00:26:02.200
No, no, I cannot take it, no, I cannot take
it!”

00:26:02.200 --> 00:26:06.539
So he went to another fellow, he was nicely
eating his food.

00:26:06.539 --> 00:26:07.620
He said, “Yes!

00:26:07.620 --> 00:26:11.980
I knew, you see, I just told you because you
asked me if you have to tell you anything,

00:26:11.980 --> 00:26:14.389
I knew God will send my food and everything.

00:26:14.389 --> 00:26:15.460
I’m quite alright."

00:26:15.460 --> 00:26:18.059
He said, “Did you see anything wondrous
there?”

00:26:18.059 --> 00:26:25.289
He said, “I saw the wonder of wonders, miracles
of miracles, that God passed a camel through

00:26:25.289 --> 00:26:28.570
the eye of a needle!”

00:26:28.570 --> 00:26:30.230
He said, “What is so miraculous?

00:26:30.230 --> 00:26:31.230
He is God!

00:26:31.230 --> 00:26:32.230
He’s God Almighty!

00:26:32.230 --> 00:26:33.230
What?

00:26:33.230 --> 00:26:35.929
He can pass even Universes after Universes
through that hole!

00:26:35.929 --> 00:26:37.970
What is it for God?

00:26:37.970 --> 00:26:39.799
He is God Almighty don’t you understand
God Almighty?

00:26:39.799 --> 00:26:42.200
Because you have met Him, you think He’s
nothing!

00:26:42.200 --> 00:26:47.640
Because you did it so easily, you think He’s
nothing!

00:26:47.640 --> 00:26:50.509
Because He behaves like [that] you think He’s
nothing!

00:26:50.509 --> 00:26:52.240
He’s God Almighty!

00:26:52.240 --> 00:26:53.409
So what?

00:26:53.409 --> 00:26:55.700
to Him, what is it?”

00:26:55.700 --> 00:27:01.509
Then
he realised.

00:27:01.509 --> 00:27:02.509
This is Faith.

00:27:02.509 --> 00:27:05.799
That is what is enlightened within you with
puja.

00:27:05.799 --> 00:27:10.100
Not your rationality which is brought down
actually quite a lot.

00:27:10.100 --> 00:27:16.840
So with this idea, tomorrow, we’ll have
the puja, alright?

00:27:16.840 --> 00:27:21.330
May God Bless You.

