Sahaja Yogi: Jane just started labour, for
the baby.

00:27:31.440 --> 00:27:35.929
Shri Mataji: Has started?

00:27:35.929 --> 00:27:39.299
Good, good, good.

00:27:39.299 --> 00:27:43.789
It will work out.

00:27:43.789 --> 00:27:51.529
In Jane’s case she never wanted a baby – big
problem, you see.

00:27:51.529 --> 00:27:57.720
Funny ideas about children are developing
in this horrible country, which is so shocking,

00:27:57.720 --> 00:27:59.279
so shocking.

00:27:59.279 --> 00:28:06.249
I mean the mother is the one who should have
feelings.

00:28:06.249 --> 00:28:10.509
Every day you read such horrible stories about
these mother’s.

00:28:10.509 --> 00:28:11.730
Can’t imagine!

00:28:11.730 --> 00:28:18.830
They can be so cruel?

00:28:18.830 --> 00:28:23.750
The more I read about these things, one can’t
understand.

00:28:23.750 --> 00:28:25.690
How can they be cruel?

00:28:25.690 --> 00:28:33.679
I mean if you hear a little thorn has gone
into the feet of a child your heart starts

00:28:33.679 --> 00:28:38.990
melting, you know.

00:28:38.990 --> 00:28:44.309
Innocence, is attack on innocence.

00:28:44.309 --> 00:28:48.179
The whole country is after innocence.

00:28:48.179 --> 00:28:55.549
Is old men running after young girls, all
this is attack on innocence.

00:28:55.549 --> 00:29:03.000
I mean, extremely satanic, very satanic forces
are let loose.

00:29:03.000 --> 00:29:15.250
They are attacking all the children of the
world and everything.

00:29:15.250 --> 00:29:16.250
Yogini: Would You like some tea, Mother?

00:29:16.250 --> 00:29:17.250
Would you like some tea?

00:29:17.250 --> 00:29:20.110
Shri Mataji: No, but I think we’ll have
food.

00:29:20.110 --> 00:29:21.200
Better to have food.

00:29:21.200 --> 00:29:25.120
I’ve got some food for you.

00:29:25.120 --> 00:29:36.210
Heat it up and I hope you’ll like it.

00:29:36.210 --> 00:29:39.179
Now.

00:29:39.179 --> 00:29:43.809
Got something for her.

00:29:43.809 --> 00:30:03.820
Can you imagine where people are killing their
wives, their husbands?

00:30:03.820 --> 00:30:08.549
Yesterday, today, My husband was telling Me
there was a case where a wife was killed and

00:30:08.549 --> 00:30:11.539
was put in the fridge, deep freeze.

00:30:11.539 --> 00:30:14.139
Can you imagine?

00:30:14.139 --> 00:30:18.789
And then Peter (Pierce) told another story
that a lady delivered her child in the loo

00:30:18.789 --> 00:30:20.509
and left the child [to] die there.

00:30:20.509 --> 00:30:22.840
I mean, this kind of people can you imagine?

00:30:22.840 --> 00:30:26.519
They have only sex-love and a sort of dirty
feelings for others, they have never good,

00:30:26.519 --> 00:30:29.039
pure feelings for anyone else.

00:30:29.039 --> 00:30:32.570
What should you say to such people?

00:30:32.570 --> 00:30:34.590
I just can’t understand.

00:30:34.590 --> 00:30:35.600
Very destructive.

00:30:35.600 --> 00:30:36.600
Satanic.

00:30:36.600 --> 00:30:41.480
You see but there must be something satanic
in people to accept such satanic things.

00:30:41.480 --> 00:30:47.659
I mean I cannot think of one case in India
– one case – where a mother could kill

00:30:47.659 --> 00:30:48.659
the child.

00:30:48.659 --> 00:30:50.149
One case I cannot think.

00:30:50.149 --> 00:30:54.960
Even if it’s a illegitimate child she would
not like to kill but others may like to finish

00:30:54.960 --> 00:30:56.549
it off.

00:30:56.549 --> 00:31:01.320
That’s different, but she would not.

00:31:01.320 --> 00:31:08.470
I mean just can’t think of such a thing.

00:31:08.470 --> 00:31:09.470
Unbelievable!

00:31:09.470 --> 00:31:10.470
Unbelievable.

00:31:10.470 --> 00:31:14.830
They are so egoistical, so foolish.

00:31:14.830 --> 00:31:15.830
Donkeys they could be only.

00:31:15.830 --> 00:31:20.759
At the most donkeys are like that, I think,
that’s why Christ rode on the donkeys.

00:31:20.759 --> 00:31:24.110
Donkeys, are they egoistical?

00:31:24.110 --> 00:31:29.970
I don’t think so, they are not.

00:31:29.970 --> 00:31:35.480
Moreover they are not also full of hatred,
donkeys are not full of hatred.

00:31:35.480 --> 00:31:38.840
They are stupid people.

00:31:38.840 --> 00:31:42.409
You see, somebody must bully them then they
are alright.

00:31:42.409 --> 00:31:49.330
The bullying starts like this: a French bullies
English, I have seen it, puts them down.

00:31:49.330 --> 00:31:55.340
French think they are higher than the [English].

00:31:55.340 --> 00:31:58.009
See the gradation is in the opposite direction.

00:31:58.009 --> 00:32:01.740
They think that the English are lower; I think
definitely English are better than French

00:32:01.740 --> 00:32:10.889
as far as evolution is concerned, but the
French have put them down.

00:32:10.889 --> 00:32:14.159
Yesterday I met – there was one Bangladeshi
who was going back to Bangladesh.

00:32:14.159 --> 00:32:15.730
He says, “Many have gone from here.

00:32:15.730 --> 00:32:19.899
People don’t know how many have gone; if
they write it down they’ll be amazed, because

00:32:19.899 --> 00:32:20.899
they are fed up."

00:32:20.899 --> 00:32:24.740
And funny, funny things, you see he told Me,
he lived with four types of neighbours and

00:32:24.740 --> 00:32:26.900
he got so fed up with them.

00:32:26.900 --> 00:32:32.860
First neighbour he lived with, you see, he
said that, “He had a daughter and I had

00:32:32.860 --> 00:32:35.809
a daughter of the same age, 14 years of age.

00:32:35.809 --> 00:32:37.369
And he [the Englishman] said ‘Why shouldn’t
we exchange our daughters, you see, for lovemaking?’

00:32:37.369 --> 00:32:41.269
“ He got so angry and he ran away.

00:32:41.269 --> 00:32:44.190
Shri Mataji laughing: How can he?

00:32:44.190 --> 00:32:46.940
This was the first thing.

00:32:46.940 --> 00:32:52.490
Then the second one was, he said that, You
see, his daughter was – little nausea she

00:32:52.490 --> 00:32:53.559
had or something.

00:32:53.559 --> 00:32:55.340
She’s just 14 or something.

00:32:55.340 --> 00:33:00.039
So she went to the doctor and doctor said,
“Did you – have you start giving her [contraceptive]

00:33:00.039 --> 00:33:01.309
pills and things, you see?”

00:33:01.309 --> 00:33:03.330
This upset him absolutely then.

00:33:03.330 --> 00:33:07.919
Like that he gave Me four horrible instances,
the two others I cannot tell you to what extent

00:33:07.919 --> 00:33:08.919
it is.

00:33:08.919 --> 00:33:11.909
He said, “I’m not going to live in this
country."

00:33:11.909 --> 00:33:18.730
I mean, they are just like stud-bulls going
round, I tell you – horrible.

00:33:18.730 --> 00:33:20.190
And the women I don’t know what to call
them!

00:33:20.190 --> 00:33:21.190
What is the parallel?

00:33:21.190 --> 00:33:22.309
(laughing) Hawkers?

00:33:22.309 --> 00:33:23.509
Or what?

